          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "number": 2,
      "title": "太...了 — Too / Excessively",
      "explanation": "太...了 expresses that something is excessive or beyond a normal degree. Formula: 太 + Adjective + 了. For example: 太冷了 (too cold), 太快了 (too fast). The 了 at the end is required in this pattern.",
      "examples": [
        {
          "chinese": "你穿太少了。",
          "pinyin": "Nǐ chuān tài shǎo le.",
          "english": "You wear too little."
        },
        {
          "chinese": "今天太热了！",
          "pinyin": "Jīn tiān tài rè le!",
          "english": "Today is too hot!"
        }
      ],
